### RustLink API — quick manual tests (VS Code "REST Client" extension)
### Set @secret to match WEBHOOK_SECRET in your .env (leave header off if empty).

@base = http://localhost:3000
@secret = change-me

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### API info
GET {{base}}/

### Send a Rust event — Small Oil Rig spawns, respawns in ~30 min
POST {{base}}/webhook/rust
Content-Type: application/json
x-webhook-secret: {{secret}}

{
  "server": "Atlas - EU 2X Medium",
  "event": "oil_rig_small",
  "status": "spawned",
  "spawn_time": 1718614800,
  "next_respawn": 1918631200,
  "timestamp": "2024-06-17T10:00:00Z"
}

### List all timers
GET {{base}}/timers

### List timers for one server
GET {{base}}/timers?server=Atlas - EU 2X Medium

### Manually set a timer (Patrol Heli in 25 min)
POST {{base}}/timers/set
Content-Type: application/json
x-webhook-secret: {{secret}}

{ "server": "Atlas - EU 2X Medium", "event": "heli", "minutes": 25 }

### Recent event history
GET {{base}}/events

### Tracked servers
GET {{base}}/servers
